# index.json is a GENERATED artifact — the flow-store dev-server plugin
# regenerates it from a fresh scan on every write (see
# docs/superpowers/specs/2026-05-20-flow-persistence-design.md). It is not
# committed: it mutates (timestamps) on every dev-server GET and would create
# constant churn. An M5 deck build regenerates it via the same buildIndex().
index.json

# smoke-e2e/ is a throwaway flow-set the designer Playwright e2e seeds + tears
# down (test/imperative-renderer.spec.js). The slug is SLUG_RE-valid (/^[a-z0-9-]+$/)
# so the dev-server store actually scans it. Gitignored so the set-preview smoke's
# live transition tuning (which the debounced transitionSaver persists to set.json)
# never dirties the working tree.
smoke-e2e/
